104
00:09:40,246 --> 00:09:41,497
Just say you're glad if you are.

105
00:09:42,415 --> 00:09:44,250
Why would I be glad?

106
00:09:46,794 --> 00:09:51,257
Performing public duty
is my job as a public official.

107
00:09:51,340 --> 00:09:53,467
It can't be used as a means
to achieve self-realization.

108
00:09:55,261 --> 00:09:56,554
-Yes, sir.
-Yes, sir.

109
00:10:00,641 --> 00:10:04,353
However,
you're not public officials but students.

110
00:10:05,187 --> 00:10:07,148
So I suppose you could be happy about it.

111
00:10:08,608 --> 00:10:09,900
You didn't do so bad,

112
00:10:09,984 --> 00:10:11,861
considering it was
your first practical training.

113
00:10:13,904 --> 00:10:16,532
-Professor Kwon.
-Did you just say we did well?

114
00:10:18,868 --> 00:10:21,787
No. I said it wasn't bad.

115
00:10:39,013 --> 00:10:40,890
Thank you for taking me home.

116
00:10:40,973 --> 00:10:42,350
I should be the one to thank you.

117
00:10:42,433 --> 00:10:45,019
Thanks to you, I got to drive fast.
It was so satisfying.

118
00:10:45,102 --> 00:10:47,688
Me too.
Especially when you did the drifting,

119
00:10:47,772 --> 00:10:49,482
it relieved all of my stress.

120
00:10:50,066 --> 00:10:52,026
What? Are you the younger version of me?

121
00:10:53,194 --> 00:10:55,029
I hope you'll enjoy
the rest of your vacation.

122
00:10:55,112 --> 00:10:57,031
Enjoy your dates with Sun-ho as well.

123
00:10:58,157 --> 00:10:59,241
Sorry?

124
00:10:59,325 --> 00:11:00,993
Why do you look so surprised?

125
00:11:01,077 --> 00:11:03,871
Everyone knows that you two are dating,
except for Beom-tae.

126
00:11:14,465 --> 00:11:16,759
You should drive back safely.

127
00:11:18,677 --> 00:11:22,306
I want to see you more often
for a long time.

128
00:11:24,642 --> 00:11:26,519
I'll see you next semester.

129
00:11:45,454 --> 00:11:48,332
Are you going to Seoul Metropolitan
Police Agency right away?

130
00:11:48,416 --> 00:11:51,710
Yes. I need to write them
a witness statement.

131
00:11:51,794 --> 00:11:54,255
Oh, right. Remember the guy

132
00:11:54,338 --> 00:11:55,965
