01:04:33,327 --> 01:04:34,328
Who are you?

822
01:04:41,627 --> 01:04:43,170
SUSPECT INTERVIEW REPORT

823
01:04:45,298 --> 01:04:47,008
NAME: KANG SUN-HO

824
01:04:47,091 --> 01:04:49,135
-Your name.
-Kang Sun-ho.

825
01:04:49,218 --> 01:04:51,554
-Age.
-We're 19.

826
01:04:51,637 --> 01:04:53,764
Profession, high school student.

827
01:04:53,848 --> 01:04:55,308
Address?

828
01:04:55,391 --> 01:04:58,394
Namyang-dong 37-1, Jongno-gu, Seoul.

829
01:05:06,944 --> 01:05:11,240
Officer Yu Dong-man let off
Kang Sun-ho, the hacker.

830
01:05:12,199 --> 01:05:13,367
YU DONG-MAN

831
01:05:15,077 --> 01:05:16,913
Did he help you?

832
01:05:21,542 --> 01:05:23,377
Who are you?

833
01:06:07,630 --> 01:06:09,256
Was his name Kang Sun-ho?

834
01:06:09,340 --> 01:06:11,175
He's an interesting character.

835
01:06:11,258 --> 01:06:13,678
I guess you're fond of him, right?

836
01:06:13,761 --> 01:06:17,014
The case of the illegal gambling ring.
I don't think we are done yet.

837
01:06:17,098 --> 01:06:19,684
Be honest with me.
Is there something I should know?

838
01:06:19,767 --> 01:06:21,435
Do as I say.

839
01:06:21,519 --> 01:06:23,479
Nothing will happen, right?
Everything will be okay, right?

840
01:06:23,562 --> 01:06:25,815
Will you join hands with me and live?

841
01:06:25,898 --> 01:06:28,901
Or will you fall off the cliff
with Yu Dong-man?

842
01:06:28,985 --> 01:06:31,445
The choice is yours, Kang Sun-ho.

